Article 3
Promoting ideas such as indifference to life or self-deprecation;
Promoting a distorted outlook on the world, life, or values;
Promoting negative values ​​such as extravagance and hedonism, flaunting and aggrandizing wealth, and passive decadence;
Promoting distorted aesthetics, the grotesque, and vulgar culture;
Promoting pseudoscientific content such as absurd and fantastic claims, alarmism,  and fortune-telling numerology;
Promoting    negative views on   romance   and friendship   for minors;
Information promoting ideas such as “the theory that studying is useless”, “studying only for grades”, and “studying only to get higher degrees”.
Other content with a negative value orientation contrary to public order, good custom, and social mores.
Article 4
Having minors speak or act in age-inappropriate ways;
Using minors’ images to enact scenes with bad values or inappropriate content;
Using minors’ voices to disseminate negative content;
Using minors’ images to advertise goods and services not suitable for minors;
Drawing traffic by pranking or mocking minors, or by making them divisive figures;
Including minors in short videos for long periods to draw attention,  disrupting minors’ lives .
Testing minors’ character or morality,   in negative ways or for negative reason  s  amplifying bad trends and emotions;
Distorting or sensationalizing illegal activity involving minors;
Other improper use of minors’ images
